---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Nav from '../../components/Nav.astro';
import Footer from '../../components/Footer.astro';
---
<Layout lang="en" title="Privacy Policy — Fab Verbatim" description="Privacy policy of Fab Verbatim in compliance with the GDPR and LOPDGDD.">
  <Nav lang="en" currentPage=""/>
  <main>
    <div class="page-hero"><div class="page-hero-inner reveal"><p class="eyebrow eyebrow--light">Legal</p><h1>Privacy Policy</h1><p>Regulation (EU) 2016/679 — GDPR · Organic Law 3/2018 — LOPDGDD</p></div></div>
    <section class="legal-body">
      <div class="legal-inner reveal">
        <p class="legal-intro">In compliance with Regulation (EU) 2016/679 of the European Parliament and of the Council of 27 April 2016 on the protection of natural persons with regard to the processing of personal data (GDPR), and Organic Law 3/2018 of 5 December on the Protection of Personal Data and guarantee of digital rights (LOPDGDD), users of this website are informed about the privacy policy and personal data processing.</p>
        <div class="legal-section"><h2 class="legal-h2">1. Data controller</h2><div class="legal-data-grid"><div class="legal-data-row"><span class="legal-data-label">Controller</span><span class="legal-data-val">Fabienne Colette Marie Françoise Annys</span></div><div class="legal-data-row"><span class="legal-data-label">Trading name</span><span class="legal-data-val">Fab Verbatim</span></div><div class="legal-data-row"><span class="legal-data-label">NIF</span><span class="legal-data-val">X1233450Y</span></div><div class="legal-data-row"><span class="legal-data-label">Address</span><span class="legal-data-val">Carrer Sant Pere nº 7, Sant Climent de Llobregat, 08849 Barcelona, Spain</span></div><div class="legal-data-row"><span class="legal-data-label">Email</span><span class="legal-data-val"><a href="mailto:contact@fabverbatim.com">contact@fabverbatim.com</a></span></div></div></div>
        <div class="legal-section"><h2 class="legal-h2">2. Purpose of data processing</h2><p class="legal-p">Personal data voluntarily provided by the user through the contact form will be used to: manage enquiries or requests made by the user; and establish communications for the provision of services or sending of requested information.</p></div>
        <div class="legal-section"><h2 class="legal-h2">3. Legal basis</h2><p class="legal-p">The legal basis for processing your data is the user's consent when completing the contact form and accepting this privacy policy.</p></div>
        <div class="legal-section"><h2 class="legal-h2">4. Data processed</h2><p class="legal-p">The personal data processed will be that provided by the user through the contact form: full name, email address, and any other information included in the message. Data will be treated confidentially and will not be used for purposes other than those indicated.</p></div>
        <div class="legal-section"><h2 class="legal-h2">5. Retention period</h2><p class="legal-p">Personal data will be retained for the time necessary to manage the enquiry and/or relationship established with the user, and in any case until deletion is requested.</p></div>
        <div class="legal-section"><h2 class="legal-h2">6. Recipients</h2><p class="legal-p">Personal data will not be shared with third parties, except by legal obligation or where necessary for the provision of a service requested by the user.</p></div>
        <div class="legal-section"><h2 class="legal-h2">7. User rights</h2><div class="rights-grid"><div class="right-card"><div class="right-name">Access</div><div class="right-desc">Know what personal data is being processed.</div></div><div class="right-card"><div class="right-name">Rectification</div><div class="right-desc">Request correction of inaccurate data.</div></div><div class="right-card"><div class="right-name">Erasure</div><div class="right-desc">Request deletion of data when no longer necessary.</div></div><div class="right-card"><div class="right-name">Restriction</div><div class="right-desc">Restrict the use of data in certain cases.</div></div><div class="right-card"><div class="right-name">Objection</div><div class="right-desc">Object to processing of your data on grounds relating to your particular situation.</div></div><div class="right-card"><div class="right-name">Portability</div><div class="right-desc">Receive your data in a structured format and transmit it to another controller.</div></div></div><p class="legal-p" style="margin-top:1.2rem">To exercise these rights, please contact <a href="mailto:contact@fabverbatim.com">contact@fabverbatim.com</a>, stating your request and enclosing a copy of your identity document.</p></div>
        <div class="legal-section"><h2 class="legal-h2">8. Security</h2><p class="legal-p">The necessary technical and organisational security measures have been adopted to ensure the protection of personal data and prevent its alteration, loss, processing or unauthorised access.</p></div>
        <div class="legal-section"><h2 class="legal-h2">9. Complaints</h2><p class="legal-p">If you consider that the processing of your personal data infringes regulations, you have the right to lodge a complaint with the Spanish Data Protection Agency (<a href="https://www.aepd.es" target="_blank" rel="noopener">www.aepd.es</a>).</p></div>
        <div class="legal-cta"><p>Questions about how your data is handled?</p><a href="mailto:contact@fabverbatim.com" class="btn-primary">Contact me →</a></div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
  <Footer lang="en"/>
</Layout>
<style>
  .legal-body{background:var(--white);padding:5rem 4rem}.legal-inner{max-width:820px;margin:0 auto}.legal-intro{font-size:0.97rem;font-weight:300;color:#2a2a2a;line-height:1.9;margin-bottom:1.2rem}.legal-section{margin-top:2.5rem;padding-top:2.5rem;border-top:1px solid var(--border)}.legal-h2{font-family:var(--serif);font-size:1.2rem;font-weight:700;color:var(--navy);margin-bottom:1rem;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.04em}.legal-p{font-size:0.95rem;font-weight:300;color:#2a2a2a;line-height:1.9;margin-bottom:0.9rem}.legal-p a{color:var(--gold);text-decoration:underline;text-underline-offset:3px}.legal-data-grid{display:flex;flex-direction:column;border:1px solid var(--border);margin-top:1rem}.legal-data-row{display:grid;grid-template-columns:160px 1fr;border-bottom:1px solid var(--border)}.legal-data-row:last-child{border-bottom:none}.legal-data-label{font-size:0.75rem;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:0.08em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--navy);padding:0.85rem 1rem;background:var(--blue-tint);border-right:1px solid var(--border)}.legal-data-val{font-size:0.9rem;font-weight:300;color:#2a2a2a;padding:0.85rem 1rem}.legal-data-val a{color:var(--gold)}.rights-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr);gap:1px;background:var(--border);border:1px solid var(--border);margin-top:1rem}.right-card{background:var(--white);padding:1.2rem 1.3rem;transition:background 0.2s}.right-card:hover{background:var(--blue-tint)}.right-name{font-family:var(--serif);font-size:0.95rem;font-weight:700;color:var(--navy);margin-bottom:0.4rem}.right-desc{font-size:0.82rem;font-weight:300;color:var(--muted);line-height:1.65}.legal-cta{margin-top:3rem;padding:2rem 2.5rem;background:var(--blue-tint);border:1px solid var(--border);border-left:4px solid var(--gold);display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;gap:2rem;flex-wrap:wrap}.legal-cta p{font-size:1rem;font-weight:400;color:var(--navy)}
  @media(max-width:900px){.legal-body{padding:4rem 1.5rem}.legal-data-row{grid-template-columns:1fr}.legal-data-label{border-right:none;border-bottom:1px solid var(--border)}.rights-grid{grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr}.legal-cta{flex-direction:column;align-items:flex-start}}
  @media(max-width:480px){.rights-grid{grid-template-columns:1fr}}
</style>
<script>const obs=new IntersectionObserver((e)=>{e.forEach((en,i)=>{if(en.isIntersecting)setTimeout(()=>en.target.classList.add('visible'),i*60)});},{threshold:0.07});document.querySelectorAll('.reveal').forEach(el=>obs.observe(el));</script>
